#

French Herb-Crusted Pork Tenderloin

$25
450 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Main CoursePorkElegantComfort Food

Description

A succulent pork tenderloin encrusted with aromatic herbs, served with a luxurious pork gravy that elevates every bite.

Ingredients

  • Pork Tenderloin: 1.5 lbs
  • Fresh Thyme: 2 tbsp
  • Fresh Rosemary: 2 tbsp
  • Garlic: 4 cloves
  • Olive Oil: 3 tbsp
  • Salt: 1 tsp
  • Black Pepper: 1 tsp
  • Chicken Broth: 2 cups
  • Butter: 2 tbsp
  • Flour: 2 tbsp
